WHAT IS "COMMERCIAL USE"

Commercial use means any use intended for or resulting in commercial
advantage or monetary compensation. This includes but is not limited to:

  - Deploying this software as a paid or freemium service for other users
  - Using this software within a business to serve customers or clients
  - Integrating this software into a product offered to the public
  - Using this software as part of a consulting or freelance engagement
    delivered to a paying client

The following are NOT considered commercial use:

  - Running this software on your own machine for your personal job search
  - Sharing the source code on GitHub for others to study (with this License)
  - Using this software internally at a company solely for your own job
    search, where no revenue is derived from the software itself

